# Relay Project Status Tracker

The living project state and roadmap live in [`.cursor/relay-project-status.md`](../relay-project-status.md).

- **Before** starting significant work, read that file to understand current operational state and priorities.
- **After** completing roadmap items, shipping milestones, or changing priorities, update task checkboxes and the "Last updated" date in that file.
- Do not duplicate the full roadmap here; keep detailed status only in `relay-project-status.md`.
